window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>You are the name others call you. Barbarian, mercenary, fighter, lover, killer, thief, prince...God Killer.</p> <p>Emperors call him friend. He wanted to retire - now he wears a target on his back. Rumors of dungeons raided, dragons robbed, emperors showering him with gratitude.</p> <p>Back in the city of Verenvan, Skharr is attacked.</p> <p>Not willing to leave him alone, his enemies have made a grave mistake.</p> <p>Because like a dragon, one should leave a DeathEater asleep.</p> <p>Now, they have awakened The Barbarian of Theros....</p> <p>And unlike his deity, there is no mercy in his soul.</p>"; 
